              "free_text": [
                "Proton-tritium. The neutrons were obtained by",
                " bombarding a tritium gas target 3 cm long, filled to",
                " a pressure of 0.8 kp/cm2. The mean current on the",
                " target was about 0.8 mu-A in most experiments."
              ]
            }
          ],
