                "                          spread was +- 40 keV"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The scatterers were cylinders of natural elements with",
                " 2.5 cm outer diam., 0.9 cm inner diam., and an axial",
                " thickness of 2.5 cm, positioned with their axis",
                " perpendicular to that of the detector."
              ]
